---
title: Mussels in Shallot Broth with Crispy Herbed Fries and Toasted Ciabatta
description: Quick and simple, a meal of 'Moules Frites' is French food at its best! Enjoy tender mussels in the classic flavour combination of shallots and garlic with crisp and golden herb-tossed fries. Garlic mayo makes a bold and creamy dip for potatoes. Soak up the fragrant broth with toasted ciabatta.
